<noinclude>
=Add new area to Hitchwiki=
Areas can refer to pages that are neither ''cities'' nor ''countries''.

Pages for locations such as airport, road, continent, border crossing, or region.

{{#forminput:form=Area|Placeholder=Area name|autocomplete on category=Areas}}
<small>If an area with that name already exists, you will be sent to a form to edit that page.</small>

